Subject: [PATCH] stripe: wire live Payment Link URLs into audit-quiz +
 thank-you

Replaces buy.stripe.com/placeholder-ai-{specialist,team,department} with the real Payment Links generated 2026-05-13 by scripts/stripe_setup_v2_paymentlinks.py. Quiz tier-mapping and post-booking continue-now CTAs now route to live Stripe checkout. Webhook endpoint we_1TWcy9 -> https://webhook.efficio.tech/stripe/webhook registered with the 5 onboarding events; signing secret written to .env. Idempotent: re-running the helper is a no-op.
---
 audit-quiz.html | 6 +++---
 thank-you.html  | 6 +++---
 2 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/audit-quiz.html b/audit-quiz.html
index 1a388a6..620e0d3 100644
--- a/audit-quiz.html
+++ b/audit-quiz.html
@@ -546,9 +546,9 @@ ul{list-style:none}
   var CALENDLY_URL = 'https://calendly.com/brady-bngcent/efficio-strategy-call';
   // Stripe placeholder — Brady to wire actual price IDs:
   var STRIPE_LINKS = {
-    AI_SPECIALIST: 'https://buy.stripe.com/placeholder-ai-specialist', // $997/mo
